"d Renyi(1961), HCT {Havrda, Charvat (1967), Tsallis (1988)} entropy"
d and Hill's (1973) diversity measure for given parameter value.
d Renyi and HCT are special case of Shannon entropy and tend to
d Shannon as alpha --> 1. Renyi and HCT reproduce Shannon results
"d for alpha=1, while Hillâ€™s measure equals to exponential"
d (Shannon) for alpha(1).
